org.nerd4j.csv.field

Class CSVFieldProcessContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nerd4j.csv.field.CSVFieldProcessContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CSVProcessContext

    public final class CSVFieldProcessContext
extends Object
implements CSVProcessContext
    Represents the execution context of the during the process of validating and converting fields.

    This context is used both during reading of a CSV source and during writing to a CSV target.

    This context keeps some information like:

    • The current row and column handled.
    • The original value of the field.
    • The value of the field after conversion.

    Author:
    Nerd4j Team
